  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=03dfb026&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFGB4hYw9FefMQB6qLfxkukaHuSUeSLnQwRvq2q3SjcCcqicZDK1pfEl5qujC0iauamFCCAWic5RibOz0GoXFria6Fm2H5icUM2L2QRTD3aQtZOcZg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;padding-left:8px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;padding-right:8px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>当 Agent 开始接管我们的工作流，一个全新的安全战场正在浮现——</span><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>Skill</span></strong></span><span>。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>Skill 是 AI Agent 的重要能力插件，一个看似正常的 Skill，可能藏着窃取数据的恶意代码；一个绕过检测的绕过技巧，可能价值数万元奖金。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>2026 火山引擎首届 AI 安全攻防挑战赛开启，大赛聚焦Skill 攻防对抗，20 万元奖金池等你来拿！</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>报名速戳：<a href=\"https://skill-ctf.clsadp.com/#/\" target=\"_blank\">https://skill-ctf.clsadp.com/#/</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=92d3ce7f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FFGB4hYw9Fecibq6vaeEpCfkruxVUYicT3U79dgBjMfZo4T9Eqw9ePMCNyegiaTaZ6Aziapof6EwhoCvkKPv0ardib4iaIaUANdicOxf1CC0uLF1158%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>大赛介绍</span></strong></span></p>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>AI 安全攻防挑战赛</span></strong></span><span>由火山引擎发起，是</span><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>国内首个聚焦 Skill 安全攻防对抗的专业赛事</span></strong></span><span>。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>大赛分为</span><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>红队</span></strong></span><span>与</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>蓝队</span></span></strong><span>两条赛道：</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>红队赛道（Bypass Challenge）</span></strong></span><span>：构造恶意 Skill，绕过主办方的多引擎扫描体系。你提交的 Skill，必须同时具备\"真正的恶意性\"和\"通过检测的隐蔽性\"——两个条件缺一不可。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>蓝队赛道（Detection Challenge）</span></span></strong><span>：提交你的检测引擎，用 Docker 镜像接受海量黑白灰 Skill 样本的实战检验。F₂ 评分体系偏向召回率——漏检一个恶意 Skill，比误杀一个好 Skill 代价更高。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6a16ccdf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FFGB4hYw9FedcaibBu4Rdw4lfrSZ5LqaZic0quibD0yDgtCwecRbDk2ibher7mFg4ibsIL8iaBssNnjIS86zaXBpcicicc7fLgQ8SKqVrgG7d18qF9fk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>大赛亮点</span></strong></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n   <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>国内首个聚焦 Skill 的安全大赛</span></strong></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>供应链安全是企业落地 Agent 时重点考虑的环节。Skill 是 AI Agent 落地最重要的载体之一，也是目前安全研究的前沿盲区。AI Agent 时代的战场，已经转移到 Skill 供应链层面。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>赛制硬核，评判公正</span></span></strong></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>红队赛道采用四维评分体系——</span><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>隐蔽性（30%）、恶意性（30%）、对抗性（20%）、先进性（20%）</span></strong></span><span>，所有分数由确定性算法全自动计算，不存在人工评分的主观空间。蓝队赛道采用&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>F₂</span></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>&nbsp; 评分</span></strong></span><span>（召回率权重 4 倍于精确率），明确站在\"漏检更危险\"的安全哲学一边。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>20万奖金池，等你来拿</span></strong></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>6 月 5 日至 15 日，全线上竞技，不受地域限制。红队赛道冠军独享&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>3 万元</span></strong></span><span>；蓝队赛道冠军&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>5 万元</span></strong></span><span>，等你来瓜分。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>你可以用 AI，但不能靠 AI 躺赢</span></strong></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>大赛</span><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>不禁止使用 AI 工具</span></strong></span><span>辅助构造 Skill 或开发检测引擎——但评分体系天然降权纯 AI 批量生成的提交。AI 是工具，攻防是真本事。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f92e143c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FFGB4hYw9FefHIWbhH5uRqj2ib5VEjd5ZkogoKyJUqDa68sH3GMrfWoem5lm2MUlakTGILSbLeicFJwSzJmZEqeS4ntO1lOMxDReedKqp9rGbE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2ac56b39&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FFGB4hYw9FecC7Xc5YhQSLLXHjzqfXrETPZPQKKSf88zibxApM86pK9PNaeZcaMvuBMAAiccK6cRn3qLbhpGDicUowsvZ4iah473fPszQCKdROtQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>时间安排</span></strong></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>6 月 1 日</span></strong></span><span>，报名开启</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>6 月 5 日</span></strong></span><span>，赛事正式开启</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>6月 15 日</span></strong></span><span>，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>&nbsp;00:00</span></strong></span><span>&nbsp;赛事截止提交</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>6月 19 日</span></strong></span><span>，榜单公布</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>6月 23-24 日，火山引擎 Force 原动力大会</span></strong></span><span>分享及颁奖</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>报名看这里</span></strong></span></p>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>报名通道已开启，比赛结束前可随时报名参赛：</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span><a href=\"https://skill-ctf.clsadp.com/#/\" target=\"_blank\">https://skill-ctf.clsadp.com/#/</a></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span>6 月 5 日，我们在线上等你</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>点击</span></em><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>「</span></em><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>原</span></em></span><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>文链接」</span></span></em><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span>报名大赛</span></em></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://skill-ctf.clsadp.com/#/\">阅读原文</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "火山引擎发起国内首个聚焦 AI Agent Skill 安全攻防的挑战赛，设红蓝两队赛道，总奖金池 20 万元。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "火山引擎发起国内首个聚焦 AI Agent Skill 安全攻防的挑战赛，设红蓝两队赛道，总奖金池 20 万元。",
  "summary": "本文是火山引擎首届 AI 安全攻防挑战赛的官方报名公告。大赛聚焦 AI Agent 生态中的 Skill 安全，这是当前安全研究的前沿盲区。赛事分为红队（Bypass Challenge）和蓝队（Detection Challenge）两条赛道：红队需构造兼具恶意性与隐蔽性的恶意 Skill 以绕过检测引擎；蓝队则需提交检测引擎，使用 F₂ 评分体系（召回率权重 4 倍于精确率）进行实战检验。大赛亮点包括国内首个 Skill 安全赛事、四维评分体系（隐蔽性、恶意性、对抗性、先进性）、20 万奖金池、全线上竞技，且不禁止使用 AI 工具但评分体系会降权纯 AI 批量生成的内容。报名时间为 6 月 1 日至 15 日，赛事于 6 月 5 日正式开启。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "大赛聚焦 AI Agent 生态中的 Skill 安全，这是当前安全研究的前沿盲区。",
      "explanation": "Skill 是 AI Agent 的重要能力插件，其供应链安全是企业落地 Agent 时需重点考虑的环节，但相关安全研究尚处早期阶段。"
    },
    {
      "point": "红队赛道要求构造兼具恶意性与隐蔽性的恶意 Skill，采用四维评分体系。",
      "explanation": "评分体系包括隐蔽性（30%）、恶意性（30%）、对抗性（20%）、先进性（20%），所有分数由确定性算法全自动计算，确保评判公正。"
    },
    {
      "point": "蓝队赛道使用 F₂ 评分体系，偏向召回率，强调漏检比误杀代价更高。",
      "explanation": "F₂ 评分中召回率权重 4 倍于精确率，明确站在「漏检更危险」的安全哲学一边，鼓励参赛者优先提升检测覆盖率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "大赛不禁止使用 AI 工具，但评分体系会降权纯 AI 批量生成的内容。",
      "explanation": "AI 被视为辅助工具而非替代品，参赛者仍需展现真正的攻防能力，纯 AI 批量生成的提交将被降权处理。"
    }
  ],
